  "title": "14ft Truck Driver",
  "description": "<p>We are looking for responsible Delivery Drivers (14ft Truck) to deliver orders promptly to our customers. Delivery locations include childcare centres, hotels, commercial and residential buildings. You will represent our company in a professional and efficient manner to increase our profitability and customer satisfaction.</p><p>Requirements:</p><ul><li>Proven working experience as a Delivery Driver</li><li>Valid driver’s license (Class 3 and/or 4)</li><li>Excellent organizational and time management skills</li><li>Good driving record with no traffic violations</li><li>Hardworking</li><li>Punctuality & Good attendance</li><li>Knowledge of area roads and neighbourhoods</li><li>Ability to lift heavy packages.</li><li>Ability to remain calm in stressful driving situations</li><li>A polite and professional disposition</li></ul>",
